Title: Pemetrexed Plus Oxaliplatin as Adjuvant Chemotherapy for Radically Resected Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer
Conditions: Non Small Cell Lung Cancer
Phase: PHASE2
Status: UNKNOWN
Primary outcomes: To determine the clinical feasibility rate (CFR) of 4 cycles of adjuvant chemotherapy with pemetrexed followed by pemetrexed/oxaliplatin in patients with NSCLC stage IB, IIA, IIB and IIIA after a postsurgical interval of 2-4 weeks.